In other words, an active learning algorithm can choose b extra points and get them labelled by an oracle to minimize the future expected loss. There are a few differences between our formulation and the classical definition of active learning. Classical methods consider the case in which the budget is 1 (b = 1) but a single point has negligible effect in a deep learning regime hence we consider the batch case. It is also very common to consider multiple rounds of this game. We also follow the multiple round formulation with a myopic approach by solving the single round of labelling as;

